    <h3 class="h6 mt-3">Service description</h3>
    <p>Timeframe is a calendar display application that connects to Google Calendar and renders event information on e-ink display devices. The service is available as a hosted multi-tenant application or as self-hosted software.</p>

    <h3 class="h6 mt-3">Accounts and data</h3>
    <p>When using the hosted service, you create an account and may connect one or more Google accounts to grant access to your calendar data. This data is stored on the server and used solely to render content on your display devices.</p>

