    <p>Calendar data fetched from Google is used only to display events on your connected devices. No data is sold, shared with third parties, or used for advertising. Timeframe's use of Google data complies with the <a href="https://developers.google.com/terms/api-services-user-data-policy" target="_blank">Google API Services User Data Policy</a>.</p>

